{"tid":1534604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"這是一個警告，年輕人對狗官沒有耐性，已準備暴動及流血","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:44:37.000Z","uid":167032,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8edc50c635a275d2f17127e9b177f57dbdf45943","tid":1534604,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c8/2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg/250px-2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc8%2F2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg%2F250px-2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg&h=67340ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8d2206d3dda3fca483a28e69c0306adf397771","tid":1534604,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5e39d012a4a8d564eea1a769dc3ff760c4c9f89","tid":1534604,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8edc50c635a275d2f17127e9b177f57dbdf45943","tid":1534604,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c8/2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg/250px-2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc8%2F2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg%2F250px-2010_Hong_Kong_January_01_march.jpg&h=67340ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:12:46.000Z","msg":"這次遊行最大的特色，在於越來越多年輕人上街遊行，而且當中不乏行動激烈的躁少年。有網民就認為，遊行完結後都無所得著，令他們以另類方式爭取。在遊行途中，甚至有遊行人士高舉紙牌，寫着：「這是一個警告，年輕人對狗官沒有耐性，已準備暴動及流血」的標語。<br />\n<br />\n當初以為得個講字<br />\n估唔到來真"},{"pid":"13e9f4748ad9c94c28e83d03ec2ed4956e1e383c","tid":1534604,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"有網民就認為，遊行完結後都無所得著，令他們以另類方式爭取。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7adfcd903aaf73d9889bfde34c24ac656a0e8bf","tid":1534604,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"30536f73a3cbd8e87c84818965f9cb4c06425f9e","tid":1534604,"uid":289649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"4d260fc0eb2a9e8833960959841282c4246d745a","tid":1534604,"uid":119965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"前線手足 幾時講自己係「暴動」，不嬲都係話「勇武抗爭」，小心炒車/鬼&hellip;非割席"},{"pid":"befcc3ad3d11424d062cb643884bb21578e5e919","tid":1534604,"uid":38212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"張相好撚多年前㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 望下啲狗同後面啲巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352b12f56d206ec723924b3e21f458aa93202da3","tid":1534604,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有網民就認為，遊行完結後都無所得著，令他們以另類方式爭取。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n另類方式 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}